Text:
There I really have to thank you. Not only did I not know that she did work for ATK - finding anything of her is really, really difficult.

And here you give us even 10 (in words: ten) sets...

In case someone needs/wants to know, she appeared as Angela for DOMAI, as Vila for FEMJOY (Vila), as Darina for HEGRE and as Vika AG for MET-ART.
